WEBVTT

00:02.600 --> 00:03.760
- Can I have Carlo
slaughter you a hog?

00:03.800 --> 00:06.689
A token of my appreciation
for all that you do for Margot.

00:06.740 --> 00:10.232
- (Hannibal): Was Will aware of
your intention to get pregnant?
- I'm all you have.

00:10.270 --> 00:12.670
- Will understands that
Hannibal Lecter can help him.

00:12.710 --> 00:17.272
- What Will understands is
if you can't beat him, join him.

00:17.310 --> 00:19.517
_ Freddie was investigating
a story about

00:19.550 --> 00:22.383
Will and Hannibal
committing murders together.

00:22.420 --> 00:25.389
- She was a slim
and delicate pig.

00:25.420 --> 00:27.217
- You slice the ginger.

00:31.490 --> 00:33.492
(animal bellowing)

00:49.610 --> 00:52.170
(gasping)

01:04.260 --> 01:06.251
(soft classical piano music)

01:08.260 --> 01:11.195
(bird tweeting)

01:38.560 --> 01:41.825
Among gourmands, the ortolan
bunting is considered a rare

01:41.860 --> 01:45.523
but debauched delicacy.

01:45.570 --> 01:48.164
A rite of passage,
if you will.

01:50.910 --> 01:54.573
Preparation calls for the
songbird to be drowned
alive in Armagnac.

01:54.610 --> 01:56.578
It is then roasted

01:56.610 --> 01:58.805
and consumed whole
In a smgle mouthful.

02:02.450 --> 02:04.645
- Ortolans are endangered.

02:06.820 --> 02:09.118
- Who amongst us is not?

02:10.890 --> 02:12.858
- I haven't been
gorged, drowned,

02:12.900 --> 02:14.891
plucked, and roasted.

02:14.930 --> 02:16.727
Not yet.

02:16.770 --> 02:19.193
- Traditionally,
during this meal,

02:19.240 --> 02:22.539
we are to place
shrouds over our heads,

02:22.570 --> 02:25.334
hiding our faces from God.

02:25.370 --> 02:28.203
I don't hide from God.

02:40.990 --> 02:43.220
- Bones and all?

02:43.260 --> 02:45.558
- Bones and all.

03:36.810 --> 03:40.644
After my first ortolan,
I was euphoric.

03:40.680 --> 03:43.342
A stimulating reminder

03:43.390 --> 03:45.415
of our power
over life and death.

03:48.460 --> 03:51.952
- I was euphoric
when I killed Freddie Lounds.

03:54.800 --> 03:57.928
- Tell me, did your heart race
when you murdered her?

04:01.300 --> 04:03.666
- No, it didn't.
- A low heart rate

04:03.710 --> 04:06.338
is a true_indicato_r
of one's capaCIty for Violence.

04:06.380 --> 04:08.974
Your design is evolving.

04:11.450 --> 04:14.339
Your choices affect the physical
structures of your brain.

04:16.320 --> 04:19.380
- Killing is changing
the way I think.

04:19.420 --> 04:21.456
- Yes.

04:29.470 --> 04:32.837
You must understand
that blood and breath

04:32.870 --> 04:34.929
are only elements
undergoing change

04:34.970 --> 04:37.859
to fuel your radiance.

04:37.910 --> 04:40.731
