is burning.

05:24.050 --> 05:27.588
(theme music)

05:53.980 --> 05:57.108
- Orthodontics confirmed.

05:57.150 --> 05:59.118
It's Freddie Lounds.

05:59.150 --> 06:02.825
A little bit of kerosene,
fwoomp! Incendiary journalism.

06:02.860 --> 06:04.953
- See? no scabrous crust
on her chin.

06:04.990 --> 06:08.699
She was dead
before the match was struck.
- Blood's already pooled

06:08.730 --> 06:10.891
to the lowest parts of her body.
Been dead at least 24 hours.

06:10.930 --> 06:13.797
- Freddie had a longing
to be noticed.

06:15.870 --> 06:18.964
She was noticed.
- Freddie Lounds's

06:19.010 --> 06:20.978
ultimate failing
was her inability

06:21.010 --> 06:23.706
to keep herself out
of her own stories.

06:23.750 --> 06:26.469
- (coroner): There's more
to this story.

06:26.520 --> 06:28.476
Check it out.

06:28.520 --> 06:30.738
- Severely-burned bodies
tend to split along lines

06:30.790 --> 06:33.782
of musculature,
but that looks like an incision.

06:33.820 --> 06:36.118
- That's right.
He cut out her psoas muscles

06:36.160 --> 06:38.526
with, uh, it looks like
a hunting knife.

06:38.560 --> 06:40.448
- A peculiar trophy.

06:40.500 --> 06:43.663
- Why did he burn her?

06:47.040 --> 06:49.031
- Whoever did this
was not striking out

06:49.070 --> 06:51.129
against Miss Lounds's
exploitative brand

06:51.170 --> 06:53.638
of journalism.
This is something else.

06:53.680 --> 06:55.636
This is something sacred.

06:55.680 --> 06:58.046
- Freddie Lounds had to burn.

07:01.020 --> 07:04.547
She was fuel.

07:04.590 --> 07:07.889
Fire destroys and it creates.

07:07.920 --> 07:10.582
It is mythical.

07:10.630 --> 07:13.622
She won't rise from the ashes,

07:13.660 --> 07:16.788
but her killer will.

07:20.140 --> 07:22.529
- He's the one
to be noticed now.

07:31.680 --> 07:35.047
- There's no baby.

07:35.080 --> 07:37.082
It isn't even an embryo yet,

07:37.120 --> 07:39.179
but here I am,

07:39.220 --> 07:41.882
