07:41.920 --> 07:44.923
- You conspired
with your unborn child

07:44.960 --> 07:47.793
to liberate yourself.

07:47.830 --> 07:50.765
You've_ made Will _
an unknowmg accomplice.

07:50.800 --> 07:54.531
- I got what I wanted
from Will...

07:54.570 --> 07:58.028
