what I was taking

07:58.070 --> 08:00.106
until the strip turned blue.

08:04.680 --> 08:07.513
I'm not proud of myself.

08:07.550 --> 08:11.646
- Nor should you be.

08:11.690 --> 08:14.579
You said--
- I lied.

08:21.260 --> 08:23.228
- Did you know?

08:23.270 --> 08:26.228
- I was aware of Margot's goal
of having a child.

08:26.270 --> 08:29.489
I was not aware you were
the means to achieving it.

08:33.610 --> 08:35.305
- What do you want from me?

08:35.340 --> 08:38.104
- Nothing...

08:38.150 --> 08:40.118
