as you'd like to give.

08:40.150 --> 08:43.779
- As much as_ I would like
to give?

08:43.820 --> 08:46.857
- I always thought men were an
optional extra in childrearing,

08:46.890 --> 08:51.088
so... I'm not opposed
to a male influence.

08:51.130 --> 08:53.155
As long as it's not my brother.

08:53.200 --> 08:55.998
He's not good
with children.

09:02.670 --> 09:04.763
- Come on, children.

09:08.240 --> 09:10.174
- What's your name?

09:10.210 --> 09:12.178
- Franklin.

09:12.210 --> 09:14.314
Do you like
horses, Franklin?

09:19.690 --> 09:21.954
VVhoa!
(horse whinnying)

09:32.330 --> 09:35.128
Where do you stay...

09:35.170 --> 09:38.765
Franklin?
- With Mama and Shirley.

09:38.810 --> 09:41.677
- Mama is not
your real mama, is she?

09:41.710 --> 09:43.849
- She's my foster.

09:43.880 --> 09:46.849
- Do you love Mama and Shirley?

09:46.880 --> 09:48.916
- And Kitty Cat.

09:48.950 --> 09:52.044
- And Kitty Cat, yes.

09:54.990 --> 09:58.027
Franklin...

09:58.060 --> 10:00.927
you can't stay there anymore

10:00.960 --> 10:04.020
