and Kitty Cat.

10:04.070 --> 10:06.766
You have to go away.
- Who says?

10:06.800 --> 10:09.234
- The government says.
Mama lost her job

10:09.270 --> 10:12.637
and her approval
as a foster home.

10:12.680 --> 10:14.636
You can't see her
after this week.

10:14.680 --> 10:17.706
