10:26.250 --> 10:28.787
Is there something wrong
with you?

10:32.190 --> 10:34.920
There is, isn't there?

10:34.960 --> 10:38.327
Oh, here. Here now.

10:38.370 --> 10:41.168
Here we go.

10:41.200 --> 10:43.259
Can, can you put
your head back?

10:43.310 --> 10:45.870
Just like that. Perfect.

10:45.910 --> 10:48.071
Yes.

10:48.110 --> 10:50.078
Perfect.

11:01.220 --> 11:03.757
Have a chocolate.

