21:13.000 --> 21:15.366
Wish I could give it back.

21:17.100 --> 21:19.705
-SodoI.

21:25.680 --> 21:29.969
- Occasionally, I drop a teacup
to shatter on the floor.

21:30.020 --> 21:32.909
On purpose.

21:34.920 --> 21:38.321
I'm not satisfied when it
doesn't gather itself up again.

21:42.830 --> 21:45.321
Someday perhaps,

21:45.370 --> 21:47.998
a cup will come together.

22:22.070 --> 22:24.038
- Extra parts
were harvested on-site.

22:24.070 --> 22:27.369
- Just one night in the ground,
that beats Jesus by 48 hours.

22:27.410 --> 22:29.378
- Never thought Freddie Lounds
would make it to heaven,

22:29.410 --> 22:31.742
much less get deified.

22:43.730 --> 22:46.722
- This killer is trying
to get somebody's attention.

22:48.060 --> 22:51.120
- He has direction.

22:51.170 --> 22:54.492
His chaos is getting
more orderly.

22:54.540 --> 22:57.532
- So first, he burns effigies,
and now he's assembling them.

22:57.570 --> 23:01.802
- Burning Freddie Lounds
wasn't his first effigy.

23:01.840 --> 23:05.071
Whoever killed Freddie
killed Randall Tier,

23:05.110 --> 23:07.613
mutilated him, dismembered him,

23:07.650 --> 23:09.618
and put him on display.

23:09.650 --> 23:11.618
- (James): Randall Tier
and Freddie Lounds

23:11.650 --> 23:15.484
have a connection.
- Will.

23:15.520 --> 23:18.057
Randall Tier was his suspect

23:18.090 --> 23:20.422
and Hannibal's patient,

23:20.460 --> 23:22.451
and Fr_eddie_Lounds
was investigating

23:22.500 --> 23:24.468
his murder when she died.

23:24.500 --> 23:26.968
- Fre_ddie Lounds
was investigating

23:27.000 --> 23:30.538
a lot of things,
when she died.

23:35.780 --> 23:38.908
- This psychopath was incubating
fantasies about killing

23:38.950 --> 23:41.748
and is building himself up.

23:41.780 --> 23:44.943
Or someone's building him up.

23:44.990 --> 23:49.108
- He has a benefactor
who admires his destruction.

23:54.500 --> 23:57.196
Shiva is both destroyer
and benefactor.

23:59.200 --> 24:02.658
- He's being guided.

24:02.700 --> 24:06.466
- Is this some kind
of signpost?

24:09.080 --> 24:13.517
- Maybe Freddie's killer
didn't do this...

24:13.550 --> 24:17.919
maybe his benefactor did.

24:17.950 --> 24:19.713
- Why?

24:22.190 --> 24:24.920
- It's a courtship.

24:33.540 --> 24:35.531
- (Mason): Good morning!

24:43.080 --> 24:45.173
Riding agrees with you.

24:45.210 --> 24:47.178
Puts colour in your cheeks.

24:47.210 --> 24:50.646
You've got a bloom. Really.

24:50.690 --> 24:52.646
- It's chilly.

24:57.690 --> 25:00.181
I was lying in bed...

25:00.230 --> 25:02.858
composing in my mind
like the deaf Beethoven,

25:02.900 --> 25:04.868
and it occurred to me

25:04.900 --> 25:06.959
that for a family

25:07.000 --> 25:10.197
who owns breeding stock,

25:10.240 --> 25:13.061
