much of it ourselves.

25:13.110 --> 25:15.101
I'm concerned about

25:15.140 --> 25:18.303
the next generation
of Vergers. Aren't you?

25:18.350 --> 25:21.808
- I'm just trying
to survive this generation.

25:21.850 --> 25:23.818
(Mason laughing)

25:23.850 --> 25:26.944
- Meat is, at base,

25:26.990 --> 25:29.049
a people business.

25:29.090 --> 25:32.856
